-lit escalators that sweep guests to a 40-foot high ivy-covered lobby, an enormous indoor/outdoor Private Park and a ceiling fresco by world-famous painter Francesco Clemente.  The Hudson Hotel is the next generation of Cheap Chic – stylish, democratic, affordable, young at heart and utterly cool.</p><ul><li>356 West 58th Street New York, New York 10019</li><li>Tel. 212 554 6000 Fax 212 554 6001</li><li>Reservations US 800 697 1791</li><li>Reservations International 00800 4969 1780</li></ul><a href="http://www.hotelrooms.com/Brand_Ian_Schrager_Hotels_New_York.htm">New York Hotel Reservations</a><a href="http://www.tablethotels.com/Hotel/en/105/Review/The-Hudson-Hotel/New-York-New-York-United-States/">Hudson Hotel Reservations Special Offers</a></ul></noscript><!-- Main Nav --><div id="lowerhomenav"><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="8" width="5" /><br /><div class="homenav"><span class="nav"><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com"><img src="images/MHGgray.gif" alt="Morgans Hotel Group" border="0" /></a><br /><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="3" width="5" /><br /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com" title="Morgans Hotel Group Home Page">Home</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/reserve.asp" title="Online Reservations">Reservations</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/hotels.asp" title="Hotels">Hotels</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/meetings.asp"  title="Meetings and Events Services">Meetings &amp; Events</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/play.asp"  title="Party Pictures, City Guides and Unique Mailers">Play</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/specials.html"  title="Special O